channel.description:
[b]Hello[/b], [i]First of all[/i]- It is [b]me[/b] who is the programmer I am not hiring or in need. [b]So[/b], I am a good programmer and worked on Testscape and various other [Testscape is just a listable one] servers and my work is [b]Free[/b], all I ask is to become a mod.
[b]I can:[/b] [glow=red,2,300]Add things like ::barrows to your server[/glow] [glow=red,2,300]Make Custom Quests[/glow] [glow=red,2,300]Make Magic and/or Range work[/glow] [glow=red,2,300]Many others...[/glow]
If you want to Hire me Just post here And I will sort out rest.
[i]Oh and [b]1[/b] last thing...[/i]
[glow=red,2,300]In the case of Lot's of People wanting me It will have to go for Real RS Money [directly to my bro's account][/glow]
[u]I am very Professional and do not want any guff[/u][br][size=1]Posted at: August 02, 2006, 08:23:34 AM[/size][hr]You can also email me at [b]flame-405@hotmail.co.uk[/b][br][size=1]Posted at: August 02, 2006, 08:27:24 AM[/size][hr]Actually [b]Please[/b] email me.
